{"tid":117159,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"人像攝影 ff vs apsc （canon)","createTime":"2017-02-12T03:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T13:07:18.000Z","uid":26080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fccfeb1ba90f7ab4262e79923ee47b28d9f3396","tid":117159,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"1. 散景效果<br />\n好多師兄都話影人買ff，因為散景效果更明顯。咁我本身用canon 80d, 手上有sigma 24 f1.4 , 50-100 f1.8, 17-55 f2.8（等效景深分別係f2.2, f2.8, f4）, 由其係sigma 50-100, 令我影人散景效果已經好夠用，就散景效果而言，我覺得唔一定要上ff<br />\n<br />\n2. 顏色層次<br />\n有人講影人用canon ，因為canon 紅色做得比較「好」，返而我又唔多覺，可能我睇既相唔夠人地多啦<br />\n<br />\n係Flickr 睇外國高手影既人像相，見到ff 做出黍既面部顏色會有多啲既顏色層次（紅同橙），而apsc 就會偏向白，呢個係唔係ff 既好處？<br />\n<br />\n但係我影人好鐘意係戶外3-5pm影，好鐘意太陽金黃色，似乎呢個環境下ff 又冇咩優勢<br />\n<br />\n3. 面部細致<br />\n影女：冇所謂啦，都要用ps 執，啲女係要要白滑膚色<br />\n影仔，老人：反而我又好鐘意啲細緻，什至會聞相睇下啲粉刺夠唔夠sharp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 目前部80d 同支50-100 已經好sharp, 睇唔到呢方面需要用ff<br />\n<br />\n4. Dynamic Range<br />\n3-5 pm 戶外影人係最佳時間，影逆光相好正。呢點ff 當然有優勢，如果你同我一樣係80d user, 揀高用色調優先（iso 200), 影raw, 後期推陰影收高光空間好大，有外國YouTube 拎80d 同 5d mark iii比，推陰影係80d 優勝，當然你要花小小後製時間，直出撚唔好試<br />\n<br />\n5. 夜間人像<br />\nCanon ff 冇內閃<br />\n飛燈？不了，我又唔係要搵食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以講下你上左ff 之後影人有咩好處？"},{"pid":"14766d8a38d0d28bbd3f01f100979f6845d936f2","tid":117159,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"Sorry 我個標題唔好，用緊其他牌子既巴打一齊討論啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5740166028a501b4740ebd0399701185a4207fba","tid":117159,"uid":52059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T03:56:42.000Z","msg":"自我感覺良好，成像好左<br />\nnikon ff有內閃，轉會吧"},{"pid":"8ae3c7a4446e04b68ac3b9a960f1198a9e2da9a8","tid":117159,"uid":50069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"用過外閃你返唔到轉頭<br />\n差好多"},{"pid":"cc59c1689df064af8cc70540f9b9857fe88edf7b","tid":117159,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自我感覺良好，成像好左<br />\nnikon ff有內閃，轉會吧</blockquote><br />\n80d 都有內閃<br />\n自我感受良好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成像好左即係點？"},{"pid":"020aaa2a4614a543e3793c0a1cd3f8fa10d9ad26","tid":117159,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用過外閃你返唔到轉頭<br />\n差好多</blockquote><br />\n又要入多個坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc39c4fc666fa19858a0910ffbda3181e4c91f20","tid":117159,"uid":20390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用過外閃你返唔到轉頭<br />\n差好多</blockquote><br />\n認同，我影小朋友，室內，補光用，睇唔出用左閃"},{"pid":"22ba021f645670313ead31b31e9e214b495a9022","tid":117159,"uid":52059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自我感覺良好，成像好左<br />\nnikon ff有內閃，轉會吧</blockquote><br />\n80d 都有內閃<br />\n自我感受良好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成像好左即係點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聞相時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23051075d2e2278b295242029f19b78c50471a7","tid":117159,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自我感覺良好，成像好左<br />\nnikon ff有內閃，轉會吧</blockquote><br />\n80d 都有內閃<br />\n自我感受良好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成像好左即係點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聞相時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a866bf9e8dff6b039a601fd99cb42d0fc9e14a95","tid":117159,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"留名睇内閃人像"},{"pid":"03441bfb21842aa47db6a221ac07c